---
title: Загрузка файла
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Пользователь
    participant F as files.py
    participant UT as utils.py
    participant M as models.py
    participant FS as Файловая система
    participant T as templates/

    U->>F: POST /upload<br/>file + folder_type
    F->>M: current_user.upload_blocked
    M-->>F: False
    F->>UT: get_base_path
    UT-->>F: /uploads/users/username/
    F->>UT: safe_filename
    UT-->>F: document.pdf
    F->>FS: file.save(path)
    FS-->>F: OK
    F->>F: flash success
    F->>T: redirect personal.html
    T-->>U: Обновлённая страница
